The cheaper type pumps are not "self priming" and will need to be set 
below tank level.  With rotary type pumps it is critical that they dont 
try to pump air for very long. In fact the only self priming pump i 
have seen associated with a vw is the  pump on the gas heaters.
jimt
westydriver
